      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Ḥananya, second and third-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1527\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Ḥananya\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהושע בן חנניה\">רַבִּי יְהוֹשֻׁעַ</span> אוֹמֵר: בַּשַּׁבָּת אָמְרוּ, קַל וָחוֹמֶר",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בַּחוֹל. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-518\" href=\"/bava_batra/156b#gemara-line-29\" title=\"Mishnah source: Bava Batra 156b\">כַּיּוֹצֵא בּוֹ – זָכִין לַקָּטָן, וְאֵין זָכִין לַגָּדוֹל;</a>",
